-- =============================================================
--  SCRIPT 05 — CRM & MARKETING: SEGMENTATION & SCORING
--  Domain:  Sales CRM + Marketing
--  Type:    Segmentation & Scoring
--  Dialect: Standard SQL (portable)
--
--  Models covered:
--    • RFM Segmentation (Recency, Frequency, Monetary)
--    • Lead Scoring (behavioral + firmographic)
--    • Account Health Score
--    • ICP Fit Score (Ideal Customer Profile)
--    • Segment-level benchmarks & flags
-- =============================================================


